        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Promoting Diversity and Inclusion in Banking Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires banking regulators to rate diversity and inclusion when assessing depository institutions under the Uniform Financial Institutions Rating System or a comparable rating system. </p>]]>
        </text>
